  Keywords                 = {Computer Simulation; Disease Outbreaks, prevention /&/ control; Humans; Influenza A Virus, H1N1 Subtype, pathogenicity; Influenza Vaccines, administration /&/ dosage; Influenza, Human, epidemiology/prevention /&/ control; Models, Biological; World Health},
